title: 32: Which Cartoon is the Hottest?
itunes:title: Which Cartoon is the Hottest?
description:
Trevor is back from Canada and Michael is back from Dublin. They quickly realize that the best women from around the world are actually just animations. They also talk about falling in love with a stripper and not knowing a damn thing about the government.
